00:51:54.358 --> 00:51:55.596
So here's the plan.

752
00:51:55.597 --> 00:51:58.723
You're the getaway driver.

753
00:51:58.724 --> 00:52:00.188
So you'll wait in the boat.

754
00:52:00.189 --> 00:52:02.395
Wait, hold on.
Wait in the boat?


755
00:52:02.396 --> 00:52:06.240
But... I want to be
in on the actions!


756
00:52:06.550 --> 00:52:10.676
Dru, the getaway driver is the
most crucial part of any plan.


757
00:52:10.677 --> 00:52:15.257
Do you know how hard it is
doing nothing, touching nothing,


758
00:52:15.258 --> 00:52:18.348
with all of the adrenaline
coursing through your veins…


759
00:52:18.349 --> 00:52:20.087
and you must wait.

760
00:52:20.088 --> 00:52:21.923
Can I count on you?

761
00:52:21.948 --> 00:52:23.029
Well...

762
00:52:23.054 --> 00:52:24.900
I guess so…

763
00:52:24.901 --> 00:52:28.722
So... I'll climb up the cube
and enter here.


764
00:52:28.723 --> 00:52:31.344
Then once I'm inside,
I'll find the diamond.


765
00:52:31.345 --> 00:52:35.468
I've underestimated Bratt before.
It's not going to be easy.


766
00:52:35.469 --> 00:52:38.344
I think we can handle it.

767
00:52:40.217 --> 00:52:44.035
Dad's villain suits!
This will make us unstoppable.


768
00:52:44.036 --> 00:52:46.322
Whoa.
Ay, chihuahua!


769
00:52:46.323 --> 00:52:48.278
I call the black one!

770
00:52:50.506 --> 00:52:53.433
It's go time!

771
00:53:03.135 --> 00:53:05.714
Hello.
Oh, hi.


772
00:53:05.715 --> 00:53:08.830
Hello, mother of Margo.
I am Niko.


773
00:53:08.831 --> 00:53:13.925
I present you with pig to confirm
my engagement to your daughter.


774
00:53:16.231 --> 00:53:17.771
- Hey, what now?
- What's going on?


775
00:53:17.772 --> 00:53:19.264
Remember, little boots?

776
00:53:19.265 --> 00:53:22.690
- Hello, my schmoopsie poo.
- Whoa! Hey!


777
00:53:22.691 --> 00:53:25.277
He seems to think you're engaged.

778
00:53:25.710 --> 00:53:27.936
What?
We're not engaged!


779
00:53:27.937 --> 00:53:31.018
Look, Niko.
You seem like a very nice boy


780
00:53:31.019 --> 00:53:32.565
With a very nice pig.

781
00:53:32.566 --> 00:53:35.112
Uh, but you're not engaged.

782
00:53:35.574 --> 00:53:38.191
Okay?
It's not happening.


783
00:53:38.216 --> 00:53:41.277
I understand.
Who was I kidding?


784
00:53:41.278 --> 00:53:45.358
A dumpling like me with
a goddess like you?


785
00:53:45.359 --> 00:53:49.727
But I promise:
I will never forget you, Margo.


786
00:53:49.728 --> 00:53:51.370
Never.

787
00:53:52.494 --> 00:53:55.190
Oh, I'm pretty sure
I won't forget you, either.


788
00:53:55.191 --> 00:53:57.527
Bye.
Bye, Niko.


789
00:53:57.528 --> 00:54:00.034
Wow, that was crazy!
Wooo!


790
00:54:00.035 --> 00:54:02.273
That was totally humiliating!

791
00:54:02.274 --> 00:54:05.516
Taking a bite of that cheese was
the stupidest thing I've ever done.


792
00:54:05.517 --> 00:54:06.936
Why did I listen to you?

793
00:54:06.937 --> 00:54:09.353
Right, but it's over now, so...

794
00:54:09.354 --> 00:54:12.343
Ugh, here we go.
Niko...


795
00:54:12.814 --> 00:54:16.477
You!
You refuse my son's engagement pig?


796
00:54:16.478 --> 00:54:17.105
What?

797
00:54:17.106 --> 00:54:22.535
May you and your daughter die
a slow death and be buried with onions!


798
00:54:24.389 --> 00:54:26.119
Alright, lady.
That's it!


799
00:54:26.120 --> 00:54:31.546
Nobody... nobody! ...curses my daughter!
You got that?


800
00:54:31.547 --> 00:54:34.479
Because if you mess with Margo,
you mess with me!


801
00:54:34.504 --> 00:54:39.056
And I promise, you do not
want to mess with me!


802
00:54:39.081 --> 00:54:41.442
Do you understand me?

803
00:54:41.443 --> 00:54:42.579
Yes, yes.

804
00:54:42.580 --> 00:54:45.684
Good.
Now, GET!


805
00:54:48.639 --> 00:54:51.760
Look, Margo.
I think we just need to... Oh.


806
00:54:55.056 --> 00:54:56.376
Yes!

807
00:54:56.377 --> 00:54:58.964
Oh!
I've to tell Gru!


808
00:55:14.712 --> 00:55:17.402
- Can we go back now?
- Already?


809
00:55:17.403 --> 00:55:19.131
Just a couple more hours!

810
00:55:19.132 --> 00:55:21.817
We have to be home
before it gets dark.


811
00:55:22.481 --> 00:55:24.511
I don't understand.

812
00:55:24.512 --> 00:55:26.854
I did exactly what the man said.

813
00:55:26.855 --> 00:55:30.301
You mean that one-eyed, scar-faced man
that everybody laughed at?


814
00:55:30.302 --> 00:55:32.523
Yeah.
It makes no sense.


815
00:55:32.524 --> 00:55:35.411
- Look, Agnes, maybe we're not...
- Huh!


816
00:55:46.560 --> 00:55:50.154
My whole life has been
building to this moment!


817
00:55:55.807 --> 00:55:57.061
Um.
It's a...


818
00:55:57.062 --> 00:55:59.071
Unicorn!

819
00:56:00.704 --> 00:56:03.022
I can't believe it!

820
00:56:03.247 --> 00:56:06.027
I'm gonna name you Lucky!

821
00:56:06.028 --> 00:56:09.366
Oh, Lucky, stop it...

822
00:56:10.213 --> 00:56:13.370
Yeah.
I'll let someone else burst her bubble.


823
00:56:19.802 --> 00:56:23.433
Look at us!
Two brothers pulling a heist.


824
00:56:23.458 --> 00:56:29.199
And that diamond will make us the richest,
most powerful villains in the world!


825
00:56:29.200 --> 00:56:30.907
Right, Brother?

826
00:56:31.796 --> 00:56:35.067
Right.
Yeah. Yeah...


827
00:56:36.641 --> 00:56:40.542
Bravo! Bravissimo!
You're amazing!


828
00:56:40.567 --> 00:56:42.986
I'm so sorry. I'm so embarrassed.
I was very rude.


829
00:56:42.987 --> 00:56:45.220
- And you were always such a gentleman.
- You did it! You did it!


830
00:56:45.221 --> 00:56:47.326
You got our jobs back.

831
00:56:53.240 --> 00:56:55.741
What? Oh yeah.
Right. Sure.


832
00:56:55.742 --> 00:56:57.725
Oh look, we're here!

833
00:57:04.417 --> 00:57:06.870
I'm going in.
Take the wheel.


834
00:57:06.871 --> 00:57:09.225
I still don't see
why I can't go with you.


835
00:57:09.250 --> 00:57:11.011
Hey.
Hey, we discussed this.


836
00:57:11.012 --> 00:57:13.490
Now is not the time
to mess with the plan.


837
00:57:13.491 --> 00:57:15.478
Fine...

838
00:57:28.613 --> 00:57:30.428
- Hey, brother.
- What?


839
00:57:30.429 --> 00:57:32.985
I told you, you were
supposed to stay with the boat!


840
00:57:33.010 --> 00:57:36.112
Oh, I didn't think
you meant that literally.


841
00:57:36.113 --> 00:57:38.732
What other way
could I have meant it?


842
00:57:39.137 --> 00:57:42.437
Alright. Let's move.
Just follow my lead.


843
00:57:42.438 --> 00:57:44.185
Got it.

844
00:57:47.384 --> 00:57:49.574
Help me!
Ow! Ow! Ow!


845
00:57:49.575 --> 00:57:51.619
Oh no!
The poison spikes!


846
00:57:51.620 --> 00:57:54.483
Oh, I'm gonna be impaled!

847
00:57:56.159 --> 00:57:58.694
Ha ha!
I'm okay!


848
00:57:58.834 --> 00:58:00.731
I miss the Minions.

849
00:58:00.756 --> 00:58:02.275
Come on!

850
00:58:07.969 --> 00:58:09.750
Coming.

851
00:58:15.291 --> 00:58:16.994
Coming.

852
00:58:21.246 --> 00:58:22.843
Come on.

853
00:58:28.311 --> 00:58:30.042
It's a scanning device!

854
00:58:30.043 --> 00:58:32.363
Quick... camouflage mode.

855
00:58:32.533 --> 00:58:34.534
Freeze!
And close your eyes.


856
00:58:34.535 --> 00:58:36.547
And cover your mouth!

857
00:58:42.113 --> 00:58:44.313
Okay.
Take my hand!


858
00:59:07.200 --> 00:59:10.345
Ha ha.
Follow me!


859
00:59:26.737 --> 00:59:28.232
Ha ha.

860
00:59:33.337 --> 00:59:35.362
Look out!

861
00:59:39.036 --> 00:59:42.388
You're right.
I should've stay in the boat.


862
00:59:42.389 --> 00:59:45.231
My stomach feels all queasy.

863
00:59:45.232 --> 00:59:49.271
I shouldn't have eaten
that hot pie.


864
00:59:49.449 --> 00:59:51.804
Hey. Hey.
Relax.


865
00:59:51.829 --> 00:59:55.870
You're going to be just fine.
I got your back.


866
01:00:01.988 --> 01:00:03.955
Come on, this way.

867
01:01:35.165 --> 01:01:36.935
It looks like
it's right above us.


868
01:01:36.936 --> 01:01:39.535
Okay! What do I do?
Should I wait in the vent?


869
01:01:39.536 --> 01:01:41.509
No.
Come with me.


870
01:01:56.573 --> 01:01:59.292
Yes, I'd like to
thank the Academy.


871
01:02:01.327 --> 01:02:02.947
- I can...
- No no no no no...


872
01:02:02.948 --> 01:02:05.415
- Why? I can do it.
- Don't, don't, don't!


873
01:02:05.416 --> 01:02:08.584
Yes, yes, Molly Ringwald.
I will take you to the prom.


874
01:02:08.585 --> 01:02:10.444
What... Who…
Where... What...


875
01:02:10.445 --> 01:02:12.353
Who's there…?
Who's there…?


876
01:02:19.329 --> 01:02:22.180
Ninety nine red balloons...

877
01:02:22.181 --> 01:02:24.209
Whoops!
Almost forgot.


878
01:02:34.700 --> 01:02:37.220
Shhh, shhh.
Over here!


879
01:02:38.637 --> 01:02:40.375
Stay close!

880
01:02:41.733 --> 01:02:44.540
Huh!
Whaaa...


881
01:02:44.565 --> 01:02:45.938
Dolls.

882
01:02:45.939 --> 01:02:49.822
Looks like Bratt was the only one
stupid enough to buy this junk.


883
01:02:49.823 --> 01:02:52.971
Oh.
I used to have one of these!


884
01:02:52.972 --> 01:02:55.341
Pew pew pew!

885
01:02:55.342 --> 01:02:58.233
Aaah!
Oww!


886
01:02:58.234 --> 01:03:00.653
Hey! Shh!
Come on!


887
01:03:08.009 --> 01:03:11.063
Alright.
We're getting close.


888
01:03:11.064 --> 01:03:15.654
From now on, every move must be
made with ultra precision and purpose.


889
01:03:17.233 --> 01:03:18.497
Gum!

890
01:03:18.498 --> 01:03:19.930
Focus!

891
01:03:19.931 --> 01:03:22.554
We're after the diamond,
not the bubble gum!


892
01:03:22.555 --> 01:03:24.420
Ah, got it.

893
01:03:26.531 --> 01:03:28.712
Mmm.
Yum.


894
01:03:29.619 --> 01:03:31.285
This way!

895
01:03:31.694 --> 01:03:35.201
And now to put this
where it belongs.


896
01:03:36.260 --> 01:03:37.093
What?

897
01:03:37.118 --> 01:03:40.932
Look at it, Clive.
It's beautiful!


898
01:03:46.595 --> 01:03:49.761
Will you please shut up?
He's gonna spot us.


899
01:03:51.731 --> 01:03:55.391
Spit it out! Spit it out!
I told you not to touch anything!


900
01:03:58.282 --> 01:04:01.819
Intruders! Intruders!
Intruders!


901
01:04:03.519 --> 01:04:05.646
Freeze, dipsticks!

902
01:04:05.647 --> 01:04:08.061
Gru!
There's two of you now?


903
01:04:08.086 --> 01:04:11.037
Then this will be
twice as much fun.


904
01:04:17.537 --> 01:04:19.817
Aaaaah!
Give me back my diamond!


905
01:04:19.842 --> 01:04:21.834
Total lockdown!!

906
01:04:21.835 --> 01:04:24.197
Go get 'em, Bratt Pack!!

907
01:04:32.285 --> 01:04:35.577
They're gonna get us!
They're gonna get us!


908
01:04:36.450 --> 01:04:38.672
Run!

909
01:04:47.880 --> 01:04:49.163
Oh no…

910
01:04:49.164 --> 01:04:52.327
Oh no?
What does that mean?


911
01:04:52.352 --> 01:04:55.378
ARE WE GONNA DIE??
ARE WE GONNA DIE??


912
01:04:55.403 --> 01:04:57.206
WE'RE GONNA DIE!!

913
01:05:06.663 --> 01:05:08.082
What?

914
01:05:08.369 --> 01:05:10.616
Hey, guys.
Hold on!


915
01:05:10.617 --> 01:05:12.724
Lucy!

916
01:05:19.224 --> 01:05:22.025
Thank you for saving us!
Woo!


917
01:05:22.026 --> 01:05:24.567
“Look! We got the diamond!
And we're going to...


918
01:05:24.568 --> 01:05:28.309
Take it to the AVL
and get our jobs back!


919
01:05:28.310 --> 01:05:29.112
Wait!

920
01:05:29.113 --> 01:05:30.730
What?
That's amazing!


921
01:05:30.731 --> 01:05:33.940
And the best part is
you are never ever


922
01:05:33.941 --> 01:05:37.901
go behind my back ever again!

923
01:05:37.926 --> 01:05:40.948
- Right, honeybear?
- Yeah! Yeah! Right.


924
01:05:40.967 --> 01:05:42.787
Lesson learned.

925
01:05:55.689 --> 01:05:58.296
I'll get the girls and start packing
and tell them the good news!


926
01:05:58.297 --> 01:06:00.510
Ah, we're getting
our jobs back, yeah!


927
01:06:00.511 --> 01:06:03.188
Yes. Yes.
Go tell the girls.


928
01:06:04.109 --> 01:06:04.875
Dru.

929
01:06:04.876 --> 01:06:07.989
No. No way!
We can't give the diamond back!


930
01:06:07.990 --> 01:06:10.523
- I have to.
- No, you don't!


931
01:06:10.524 --> 01:06:12.559
- Yes, I do.
- Give it.


932
01:06:12.560 --> 01:06:13.957
- No!
- Give it!


933
01:06:13.958 --> 01:06:15.874
Ow!
What is wrong with you?


934
01:06:15.875 --> 01:06:17.201
What is wrong with you?

935
01:06:17.202 --> 01:06:18.162
You kicked me!

936
01:06:18.163 --> 01:06:19.603
You
-You lied to me.

937
01:06:19.604 --> 01:06:21.566
Hey.
I would have told you the truth.


938
01:06:21.567 --> 01:06:24.513
But you're too much
of a wimp to handle it.


939
01:06:24.514 --> 01:06:26.028
That's it, I'm out of here.

940
01:06:26.029 --> 01:06:29.044
You have no right to take that,
we stole it together.


941
01:06:29.045 --> 01:06:30.837
Together?

942
01:06:31.047 --> 01:06:32.388
You got to be kidding me.

943
01:06:32.389 --> 01:06:34.631
You did nothing but
screwed up the whole time.


944
01:06:34.632 --> 01:06:36.391
I got this in spite of you.

945
01:06:36.392 --> 01:06:39.405
Oh, yeah?
Well, at least I didn't get fired


946
01:06:39.406 --> 01:06:41.792
from my job like a total loser.

947
01:06:41.793 --> 01:06:43.502
At least I had a job.

948
01:06:43.503 --> 01:06:45.599
What have you accomplished
that was so great?


949
01:06:45.600 --> 01:06:48.980
I'll tell you what:
Nothing!


950
01:06:49.002 --> 01:06:52.763
No wonder Dad thought
you were such a failure.


951
01:06:54.425 --> 01:06:56.370
We're no longer brothers!

952
01:06:56.371 --> 01:06:58.439
That's fine with me!

953
01:07:40.633 --> 01:07:44.578
Gru!
I found a unicorn!


954
01:07:46.235 --> 01:07:48.591
My life is complete!

955
01:07:50.724 --> 01:07:55.473
Honey, that's...
that's not actually a unicorn.


956
01:07:55.498 --> 01:07:56.909
Huh?

957
01:07:57.155 --> 01:08:00.939
But
-But he has one horn.

958
01:08:00.940 --> 01:08:04.033
I'm-I'm sorry, sweetie,
but...


959
01:08:04.034 --> 01:08:06.872
he's just a goat.

960
01:08:06.873 --> 01:08:10.012
Life is just like that sometimes.

961
01:08:10.013 --> 01:08:12.469
We're hoping for a unicorn

962
01:08:12.470 --> 01:08:14.932
and we get a goat.

963
01:08:16.544 --> 01:08:18.702
Well, you know what?

964
01:08:18.703 --> 01:08:22.817
Lucky is the best goat
in the whole wide world!


965
01:08:22.818 --> 01:08:27.331
Look at that face!
I just want to squeeze it.


966
01:08:31.445 --> 01:08:33.154
I'll take this.

967
01:08:33.155 --> 01:08:36.274
You've been a bad boy, Gru.

968
01:08:36.275 --> 01:08:38.314
Can you get the rest
of the suitcases?


969
01:08:38.315 --> 01:08:40.146
Come on, girls, let's go!

970
01:08:40.147 --> 01:08:44.449
Let's get physical, physical!

971
01:08:50.865 --> 01:08:52.985
Change of plan, girls.

972
01:08:52.986 --> 01:08:55.170
Instead of going home...

973
01:08:55.171 --> 01:08:57.473
Eyebrows.
Ow!


974
01:08:57.474 --> 01:09:00.883
We're going to Hollywood!

975
01:09:01.766 --> 01:09:04.988
Now that's what I call acting.

976
01:09:05.359 --> 01:09:09.283
Let's go, Clive.
We've got a giant robot waiting.


977
01:09:11.934 --> 01:09:13.266
Huh?

978
01:09:13.922 --> 01:09:16.397
Huh?
Lucy?


979
01:09:17.528 --> 01:09:19.276
Bratt, he took the girls!

980
01:09:19.277 --> 01:09:21.940
What?
No!


981
01:09:24.129 --> 01:09:26.073
Dru!
Dru!


982
01:09:26.074 --> 01:09:28.820
Go away.
I don't want to talk to you.


983
01:09:28.821 --> 01:09:31.447
Bratt has the girls!

984
01:09:37.531 --> 01:09:39.541
Listen, brother.
What...


985
01:09:39.542 --> 01:09:41.823
- About what I said.
- No, I'm the one...


986
01:09:41.824 --> 01:09:43.613
But I shouldn't have...

987
01:09:43.614 --> 01:09:46.099
I'm
-I'm sorry.

988
01:09:46.840 --> 01:09:49.299
I'm so sorry, Gru.

989
01:09:49.300 --> 01:09:51.343
Awww.

990
01:09:51.492 --> 01:09:53.256
Oh, look out!

991
01:09:53.281 --> 01:09:55.078
What is that?

992
01:10:03.138 --> 01:10:04.350
Mel?

993
01:10:40.128 --> 01:10:43.586
Hello, Hollywood!

994
01:10:43.587 --> 01:10:47.022
I'm back and bigger than ever.

995
01:10:48.331 --> 01:10:49.904
I'm scared!

996
01:10:49.905 --> 01:10:52.837
Thank you.
Thank you so...


997
01:10:58.187 --> 01:11:01.717
You can't leave me here!
I'm famous!


998
01:11:02.154 --> 01:11:05.057
Clive, arm the cannons.

999
01:11:06.954 --> 01:11:09.849
Chew on this!

1000
01:11:26.125 --> 01:11:28.787
Hey, mullet-head.
Let us out!


1001
01:11:28.788 --> 01:11:30.864
Oh, don't worry, girls.

1002
01:11:30.889 --> 01:11:34.658
I've prepared
a front row seat for you.


1003
01:11:50.121 --> 01:11:52.434
- Waaah!
- Agnes!


1004
01:11:53.293 --> 01:11:56.970
Once again, I win and Gru loses.

1005
01:11:56.971 --> 01:11:59.604
Enjoy the show, girls.

1006
01:12:06.649 --> 01:12:08.514
- What in the heck?
- Oh!


1007
01:12:08.515 --> 01:12:10.380
I hope the girls are okay.

1008
01:12:10.381 --> 01:12:11.420
Bratt!
Brother!


1009
01:12:11.421 --> 01:12:13.696
9 o'clock.
No. 3 o'clock.


1010
01:12:13.697 --> 01:12:15.579
He's on the left!

1011
01:12:17.234 --> 01:12:19.622
Huh, no.
I've seen this episode.


1012
01:12:19.623 --> 01:12:21.279
He's going to bubble gum
the whole city


1013
01:12:21.280 --> 01:12:23.428
and send it up into space.

1014
01:12:23.429 --> 01:12:25.212
Hurry!

1015
01:12:35.480 --> 01:12:37.442
This is it.
This is it.


1016
01:12:37.467 --> 01:12:39.996
Lights!
Camera!


1017
01:12:39.997 --> 01:12:41.900
LASER!

1018
01:12:51.758 --> 01:12:53.675
Yeah.

1019
01:12:59.388 --> 01:13:01.059
Look.
I got the girls.


1020
01:13:01.060 --> 01:13:02.432
You two go take care of Bratt.

1021
01:13:02.433 --> 01:13:04.555
Wait.
What are you doing?


1022
01:13:10.329 --> 01:13:11.959
Look, you guys.
It's Lucy.


1023
01:13:11.960 --> 01:13:14.376
Lucy, over here.
Help! Help us!


1024
01:13:14.377 --> 01:13:16.203
Mama's coming, girls.

1025
01:13:16.204 --> 01:13:18.650
- Lucy!
- Right here! Lucy!


1026
01:13:18.651 --> 01:13:20.229
Look at that laser go.

1027
01:13:20.230 --> 01:13:22.558
I love it when
a plan comes together.


1028
01:13:22.559 --> 01:13:25.530
Aaaah!
It's Gru!


1029
01:13:27.402 --> 01:13:28.810
Get ready, Bratt.

1030
01:13:28.811 --> 01:13:32.226
You're about to be blasted
back to the 80s.


1031
01:13:43.506 --> 01:13:46.840
Ah ho!
We got him!


1032
01:13:54.885 --> 01:13:56.259
- Oh no.
- Don't worry.


1033
01:13:56.260 --> 01:13:58.408
There's more where that came from.

1034
01:13:58.433 --> 01:14:01.072
It'll take more than
that to stop me.


1035
01:14:01.073 --> 01:14:04.177
Bratt pack,
go get that barf bag.


1036
01:14:11.669 --> 01:14:14.125
Oh, incoming!

1037
01:14:14.911 --> 01:14:16.369
Ow. Ow. Ow.

1038
01:14:16.370 --> 01:14:18.073
You, little...

1039
01:14:25.098 --> 01:14:27.150
Quick!
Jump!


1040
01:14:29.171 --> 01:14:30.568
Boners!

1041
01:14:30.593 --> 01:14:33.212
Did you see that, Clive?
All gone.


1042
01:14:33.213 --> 01:14:35.595
Bye bye, Wonder Twins.

1043
01:15:03.421 --> 01:15:04.836
Help!

1044
01:15:04.837 --> 01:15:05.964
Help!

1045
01:15:05.965 --> 01:15:07.740
Hang on!

1046
01:15:14.780 --> 01:15:17.517
Hang on, girls!
I got you!


1047
01:15:17.518 --> 01:15:20.600
I can't.
I'm slipping!


1048
01:15:21.419 --> 01:15:23.517
No!

1049
01:15:24.588 --> 01:15:26.118
Gotcha.

1050
01:15:28.158 --> 01:15:29.572
Thank you, Lucy.

1051
01:15:29.573 --> 01:15:32.179
Let's go!
We're not safe yet!


1052
01:16:00.913 --> 01:16:03.069
Look at what we have here.

1053
01:16:03.094 --> 01:16:07.916
Sorry, Gru.
This is going to be a total burn.


1054
01:16:12.434 --> 01:16:15.992
Oh, no. No!
No, no, no, no...


1055
01:16:19.652 --> 01:16:23.145
I've been a bad boy!

1056
01:16:30.387 --> 01:16:34.541
Nobody messes with my brother!

1057
01:16:37.235 --> 01:16:38.337
Aaaah!

1058
01:16:38.338 --> 01:16:40.160
Aaaaahh!

1059
01:16:45.410 --> 01:16:47.864
What?
What's happening?


1060
01:17:00.366 --> 01:17:02.626
Dru!

1061
01:17:02.736 --> 01:17:04.832
Hold on!
I'm coming!


1062
01:17:08.865 --> 01:17:11.477
You've ruined everything.

1063
01:17:11.478 --> 01:17:13.989
And now, it's time to die.

1064
01:17:13.990 --> 01:17:16.881
Any last words, Gru?

1065
01:17:16.903 --> 01:17:18.439
You know what?

1066
01:17:18.440 --> 01:17:21.359
I got two words for you.

1067
01:17:21.715 --> 01:17:23.821
Dance fight.

1068
01:17:24.249 --> 01:17:27.996
Oh, it is alright, Donkey Kong.

1069
01:17:27.997 --> 01:17:31.337
I'm going to enjoy this.

1070
01:17:50.332 --> 01:17:51.839
Enough!

1071
01:17:52.028 --> 01:17:53.661
My turn.

1072
01:18:13.275 --> 01:18:15.017
Oh oh.

1073
01:18:18.031 --> 01:18:20.117
Game over!

1074
01:18:22.294 --> 01:18:25.544
Is this what you're looking for?

1075
01:18:25.545 --> 01:18:27.136
No!

1076
01:18:27.373 --> 01:18:29.508
Ow! Ow!
Ow!


1077
01:18:36.592 --> 01:18:39.116
No...!

1078
01:18:42.164 --> 01:18:44.821
Curse you, Gru!

1079
01:18:45.068 --> 01:18:46.713
Curse you.

1080
01:18:55.596 --> 01:18:56.852
Dru.

1081
01:18:56.877 --> 01:18:58.341
Dru.

1082
01:19:05.533 --> 01:19:07.952
Hey, we did it.

1083
01:19:08.115 --> 01:19:10.639
Yes, we did, brother.

1084
01:19:10.640 --> 01:19:12.983
- Gru!
- Gru!


1085
01:19:12.984 --> 01:19:14.966
- Girls!
- Gru.


1086
01:19:28.474 --> 01:19:31.056
Hey, Mel.
Welcome back.


1087
01:20:04.051 --> 01:20:06.018
Love you, Mom.

1088
01:20:10.242 --> 01:20:13.717
I'm a Mom.
I'm a Mom!


1089
01:20:29.462 --> 01:20:31.939
Boys.
Time for bed.


1090
01:20:31.964 --> 01:20:34.146
We're back at work
in the morning.


1091
01:20:34.171 --> 01:20:37.316
- I'm coming, sweetie.
- Hi, Lucy.


1092
01:20:37.317 --> 01:20:39.057
See you tomorrow, brother.

1093
01:20:39.058 --> 01:20:42.338
Hey, I'm back on the job.
So no villainy tonight.


1094
01:20:42.339 --> 01:20:43.535
Huh, got it?

1095
01:20:43.536 --> 01:20:46.734
I make no promises.
Love you!


1096
01:20:46.735 --> 01:20:48.865
Uh-huh, right.

1097
01:20:48.876 --> 01:20:50.553
I love you too.

1098
01:20:53.427 --> 01:20:55.291
Alright, every...
Go. Go.


1099
01:20:55.292 --> 01:20:56.961
Go to bed.

1100
01:21:00.869 --> 01:21:02.936
Hey. Guys.
Come on.


1101
01:21:20.000 --> 01:21:22.028
What the heck is happening?

1102
01:21:22.029 --> 01:21:24.315
It's coming from outside!

1103
01:21:25.409 --> 01:21:25.987
Huh!

1104
01:21:25.988 --> 01:21:29.453
Hey, I thought we said
no more villainy!


1105
01:21:29.454 --> 01:21:30.782
Sorry, brother.

1106
01:21:30.783 --> 01:21:33.958
- Somebody's got to keep
the family tradition alive.


1107
01:21:33.959 --> 01:21:35.028
Right?

1108
01:21:44.843 --> 01:21:46.703
Let's get him.

1109
01:21:46.816 --> 01:21:49.205
Honey, he's my brother.

1110
01:21:49.230 --> 01:21:51.916
We'll give him
a 5 minute head start.


